1. First install 'ksquirrel-libs' package:

   a) from sources
   # tar zxfv ksquirrel-libs-0.5.0-pre4.tar.gz
   # cd ksquirrel-libs-0.5.0/
   # ./configure --libdir=/usr/lib/squirrel ** remember, that /usr/lib/squirrel is a strictly defined path!
   # make
   # su -c 'make install'
   
   b) from binary packages
RPM  # rpm -ihv ksquirrel-libs-0.5.0-pre4.rpm
TGZ  # installpkg ksquirrel-libs-0.5.0-pre4.tgz

2. Now install Ksquirrel:

   a) from sources
   # tar zxfv ksquirrel-0.5.0-pre4.tar.gz
   # cd ksquirrel-0.5.0/
   # ./configure --prefix="`kde-config --prefix`"
   # make
   # su -c 'make install'
   
   b) from binary packages
RPM  # rpm -ihv ksquirrel-0.5.0-pre4.rpm
TGZ  # installpkg ksquirrel-0.5.0-pre4.tgz
